<h3>How do I send a sympathy card?</h3>
<p>Expressions of Sympathy&trade; makes it easy for you to send condolences.  Simply select a card, personalize and sign the interior of the card, select a destination or enter a shipping address, and complete the order.  We will print and mail the card for you within one business day.<p>
<h3>What to say in a sympathy card?</h3>
<p>If you find yourself at a loss for words, Expressions of Sympathy&trade; has provided a library of sentiments to help you personalize your sympathy card. This feature will automatically appear on the personalization page.  To use, simply scroll through the Sentiment Library with the arrows and click the insert button to insert a phrase that captures your thoughts.</p>
<h3>When and how will my card be sent?</h3>
<p>Expressions of Sympathy&trade; mails cards to your recipients via U.S. Postal Service First-Class Mail within one business day.  We estimate 3-4 days delivery time.  However, delivery times vary based on postal delivery schedules and holidays. Tracking information is not available for mailed cards.</p>
<h3>Will I get confirmation of my order?</h3>
<p>You will receive an electronic receipt, including a proof of your card, at the completion of the ordering process.  Additionally, a receipt will be sent to the email address you provide during the ordering process.</p>
<h3>What if I have questions regarding my order?</h3>
<p>Please feel free to call our customer support center at 800-297-6177, M-F 8am-7pm EST.</p>
